title: Trump Not GOP Nominee — But Can Surprise Candidate Beat Clinton?
text: “Prediction markets” call the 2016 election based not on polling data, but on who bettors predict will win the presidential race, and these online gambling sites, experts say, have compiled a more accurate record of correctly predicting election winners than polls — or any other method of forecasting the winner of the presidential race.
